column1: UNC_Marchetti_diatom_cultures_all_LOBSTAHS_IDs_pos.csv, lipids identified in West Antarctic diatom isolates provided by A. Marchetti and C. Moreno, University of North Carolina
Identifications were made by J. Collins, james.r.collins@aya.yale.edu, using v1.1.1 of the LOBSTAHS lipidomics software package for R

Values in columns 14-22 of this speadsheet are raw chromatographic peak areas; the .xlsx file UNC_Marchetti_diatom_cultures_IP-DAG_pmol_totals.xlsx contains mass data for unoxidized IP-DAG obtained using authentic standards
